{"tid":1059080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁飛令越演越烈】英國丶歐盟亦加入禁飛行列 波音股價急挫","createTime":"2019-03-13T02:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T01:52:16.000Z","uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4c6ee8d6a849266d304e55462b94eb9df1f003af","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"繼早前中國丶新加坡丶馬來西亞丶澳洲下令停飛後，英國丶歐盟丶土耳其丶印度亦頒布停止737 MAX的運作及禁止相關機型飛越其領空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，墨西哥丶巴西等28個國家或地區有航空公司宣布暫停波音737 MAX 8航班嘅飛行<br />\n<br />\n另外受事件影響，波音股價連續兩日急挫，累跌超11%，本周為止波音市值已經蒸發約270億美元(約2100億港元）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據報同樣因操作737 MAX8而發生空難嘅印尼獅航計劃取消向波音訂購737 MAX，該訂單價值220億美元（約1730億港元）<br />\n<br />\n波音今次好似幾大鑊，究竟會唔會重演麥道DC-10嘅結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(小知識：麥道公司係1940-70年代同波音叮噹馬頭，係美國主要嘅飛機製造商之一，但係70年代之後，麥道公司嘅DC-10屢次發生空難，最後陷入財政困難被波音收購)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QoGVo0o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQoGVo0o.png&h=6842fd66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞航空空難之後，全球多國相繼宣布停飛同款波音737 MAX型號客機，或禁止航機飛越領空，但美國和加拿大就表明不會禁止使用。<br />\n<br />\n波音737 MAX 8客機五個月內兩度墜毀，分別造成189和157人罹難，引發客機安全疑慮。中國、埃塞俄比亞、澳洲、馬來西亞、南韓等國，以及多間航空公司相繼停飛同款客機，而擁有28個成員國的歐盟亦加入禁飛行列。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲航空安全局星期二(12日)發聲明稱，已發出停飛指令，暫停歐盟範圍內所有737 MAX 8和MAX 9機型的運作，同時禁止其他所有航班進出歐盟。而英國民航部門周二亦下令，禁止737 MAX飛機，進出或飛越英國領空。<br />\n<br />\n印度航空部門亦於今日凌晨(13日)在社交網站發文，表示已下令即時全面禁飛737 MAX型號客機，當中包括往來香港的印度香料航空。<br />\n<br />\n本港民航處亦未頒下禁飛令，指由於美國當局指737 MAX仍適合飛行，及埃塞俄比亞空難仍在調查，處方會密切留意事態發展及調查進度。<br />\n<br />\n至於波音總部所在的美國，以及加拿大就表明，不會禁制使用737 MAX客機，認為客機仍然安全並適宜飛行。<br />\n<br />\n但美國不少國會議員表示擔憂，代表美國航空2萬多名空中服務員的協會，亦強烈要求當局停飛；又指會員可選擇不在有關飛機執勤。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普亦發文稱，飛機變得愈來愈複雜，會製造危險。而波音就表示，對737 MAX系列充滿信心，又指兩宗事故有相似之處，但調查只屬初步階段，未來數周亦會提升有關軟件。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/03/13/010112012.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fnews%2Fsystem%2F2019%2F03%2F13%2F010112012.shtml&d=WTugOjWmLb2R3dS25JBA%2BUXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=e091c68b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/news/system/2019/03/13/010112012.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},{"pid":"22f174d4ac3b71a3974d8f97ecb748975e3adfbb","tid":1059080,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:20:30.000Z","msg":"侵侵又贏"},{"pid":"d41fc40747f08f81232ac9aae21a8835844c77eb","tid":1059080,"uid":85273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:26:02.000Z","msg":"如果間航空公司唔禁飛，乘客見到班機係737MAX8飛都未必敢坐，寧願揀其他航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b590e32909bfc65c95b31ad66654a749146baede","tid":1059080,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"但大部分空域不能進入，玩美加only<br />\n<br />\n新系統，完善軟件的確要時間，可惜代價太大，俾我都怕"},{"pid":"eb51aecba36a457a71d09a65323edc99c708185a","tid":1059080,"uid":80624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:28:34.000Z","msg":"明益airbus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b2291a50913de331208d917c133de20bc0811f","tid":1059080,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"eb51aecba36a457a71d09a65323edc99c708185a","tid":1059080,"uid":80624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:28:34.000Z","msg":"明益airbus<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"理性Ｄ，俾你都怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5179022fe03bbf3f42939069a37f8ba73d1f08a","tid":1059080,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34e3e7c116081adb4cb1aa21486a3b248a45532d","tid":1059080,"uid":214036,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0863195043c64cb98b3f7e8148feab4b0358edb0","tid":1059080,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e3e7c116081adb4cb1aa21486a3b248a45532d","tid":1059080,"uid":214036,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"六點起香港都停飛啦"},{"pid":"242ef467c7baad9f114f1caa15f8fc2f04c86a63","tid":1059080,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34e3e7c116081adb4cb1aa21486a3b248a45532d","tid":1059080,"uid":214036,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"佢連d manual 都係抄FAA既，仲要一字不改<br />\n如果係大學功課，一早俾人捉plagiarism <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb91d1b3e9c726fd355b6dd9500ea85aa060ddc","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b590e32909bfc65c95b31ad66654a749146baede","tid":1059080,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4d3a83c92eadf5080ac13f6664c4d8a47d9dcde0","tid":1059080,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T05:42:21.000Z","msg":"美國都未停飛 小題大做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:27:14.000Z","msg":"但大部分空域不能進入，玩美加only<br />\n<br />\n新系統，完善軟件的確要時間，可惜代價太大，俾我都怕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:39:37.000Z","msg":"依家全球停飛之後，連空域都唔俾入，即係例如我冰島去摩洛哥都唔可以經過英國同歐盟領空，咁搞法真係好多航線收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家仲飛緊737Max8嘅幾乎得返係美國同加拿大<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pSbuveC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpSbuveC.png&h=77a1ac20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"816e2cf1fe63c1bce618fb837f987aa579d5a6e1","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0863195043c64cb98b3f7e8148feab4b0358edb0","tid":1059080,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e3e7c116081adb4cb1aa21486a3b248a45532d","tid":1059080,"uid":214036,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:35:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:36:57.000Z","msg":"六點起香港都停飛啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"原本先想贊佢冇跟中國民航局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n置中國顔面何存<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過諗真啲得俄羅斯同印度飛香港有用737MAX8<br />\n依家中國同印度領空close左<br />\n佢都冇辦法繼續用落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民航處先至順水推舟話停飛，其實就係乜野都唔使做順利解決左件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2c49d1ea6c439d799c5fcca8844a2df912c53b","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWiHQiJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWiHQiJ.png&h=229a9b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾乎全部ground晒，一款機型冇理由淨係靠美國同加拿大撐住，如果遲啲調查報告冇講明係operator問題，咁Boeing就要食咗呢隻貓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一係改設計一係upgrade軟件，就算改設計都要改條生產線，無論點樣Boeing聲譽都會嚴重受損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以而家一切都等調查報告，Boeing應該好心急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47225d2840b6ad06b12a1878785dfb7da92f9528","tid":1059080,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"全世界都禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433eeba9ffb18b85d21f827edabd3e08b5fc3699","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47225d2840b6ad06b12a1878785dfb7da92f9528","tid":1059080,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"全世界都禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T07:18:36.000Z","msg":"香港六點半都禁埋 官腔到呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2544033/org/d98f19e81edf4379bea3e5eace2db496.png/XWF5YK7GNyV-z1ffYHbw0VrmtrxLzAfLXl0Rnl5dEZ4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2544033%2Forg%2Fd98f19e81edf4379bea3e5eace2db496.png%2FXWF5YK7GNyV-z1ffYHbw0VrmtrxLzAfLXl0Rnl5dEZ4&h=62d44882&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fde88abbdf52c2105bd2c3f9f6c898d6c91963cd","tid":1059080,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"816e2cf1fe63c1bce618fb837f987aa579d5a6e1","tid":1059080,"uid":219244,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0863195043c64cb98b3f7e8148feab4b0358edb0","tid":1059080,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34e3e7c116081adb4cb1aa21486a3b248a45532d","tid":10590